70010000075750.description:
Welcome to the exciting ATV racing simulator, where you will have to go through many difficult tracks full of exciting obstacles and dangerous landscapes! Get ready for an unforgettable adventure full of adrenaline and extreme!

On your way you will encounter many obstacles: steep descents, water obstacles, smooth and even unexpected traps. Be careful, because every wrong move can lead to a fall or breakdown of your ATV! From sand dunes and mountain passes to swamps and rocky routes - each new task will be a real test of your driving skills.

Use your agility, speed and attentiveness to overcome all obstacles on the way to the finish line!

Key features:
• Excellent warm-up for agility and attentiveness;
• Many tracks with varying difficulty;
• Exciting gameplay for all ages;

70010000076216.description:
You will take on the role of a fearless courier who quickly and dexterously overcomes the urban jungle on his bike. Explore various areas of the city, from densely populated streets to branching alleys. Each delivery is a new opportunity to test your navigation and route planning skills.

Be careful and avoid collisions, because falling off your bike can cost you precious time! Accelerate as much as possible, but remember about safety! Your speed can help you deliver the order on time, but do not forget to maneuver carefully to avoid accidents.

Get ready for a bike adventure where speed and caution go hand in hand. Test your skills and become the best courier in the city!

GAME FEATURES:
• A great warm-up for agility and attentiveness;
• Many missions with varying difficulty;
